{"tid":1383961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拜託各位同學仔，無rb唔好守內街","createTime":"2019-07-29T20:53:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T21:31:41.000Z","uid":57076,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5313ffebd0329e9af63c32e52ab1b987e9f67a77","tid":1383961,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T20:53:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9CnUDTO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9CnUDTO.jpg&h=d0a15bd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n發夢見到禮拜日有popo係信德射野，入晒對面條內街，有roadblock，雖然走得辛苦，但可以阻擋到popo繼續前進。<br />\n<br />\n之後大家就開始守永安附近 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無roadblock</span></span> 內街，其實有部分前線都知道要be water，因為風險真係高，而且好多人都退晒去大街<br />\n<br />\n結果就係要抬第一排中彈手足，跟住幾分鐘內再放幾粒teargas，仆街差d人踩人，有手足跌底啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95623c0c2df32ff9e73d55d7260ac126f3e65e1b","tid":1383961,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T20:56:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d109bba525b395cabfcb31ae3263f549f17b19a","tid":1383961,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T21:23:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92f15a8138815b245af49a7642ad44939086f56b","tid":1383961,"uid":269991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T21:24:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7dddb388d0d081f0779670dea7e29e7f0c7f9f30","tid":1383961,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T21:31:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}